《'''理性'''》（{{lang-en|'''''Reason'''''}}）是一個[[美國|美國]][[自由意志主义|自由意志主义]]月刊，由[[理性基金會|理性基金會]]負責發行。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://reason.org/about/ |title=Reason Foundation - About the Reason Foundation |publisher=Reason.org |date= |accessdate=2012-07-15 |archive-date=2014-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141111163215/http://reason.org/about/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 現發行量約为50,000份，<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/05/07/us/07friedlander.html |title=The New York Times . Lanny Friedlander, Founder of Reason Magazine, Dies at 63 |publisher=NYT |date= |accessdate=2012-10-15 |archive-date=2021-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314191913/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/05/07/us/07friedlander.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 被《[[芝加哥論壇報|芝加哥論壇報]]》在2003年和2004年連續評為50最佳雜誌之一。<ref>{{cite news |title=The 50 Best Magazines |url=http://www.burrmediagroup.com/50%20Best%20Magazines/ChicagoTrib_Reason061203.htm |work=Chicago Tribune |date=June 12, 2003 |accessdate=2013-07-02 |archive-date=2019-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626180951/http://www.burrmediagroup.com/50%20Best%20Magazines/ChicagoTrib_Reason061203.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=50 best magazines |url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/features/lifestyle/chi-040615mags,1,1202754.story?coll=chi-homepagenews-utl |work=Chicago Tribune |date=June 17, 2004 |accessdate=2013-07-02 |archive-date=2008-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080511075414/http://www.chicagotribune.com/features/lifestyle/chi-040615mags,1,1202754.story?coll=chi-homepagenews-utl |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 歷史==

《理性》由[[蘭尼·弗里德倫德|蘭尼·弗里德倫德]]創立於1968年，最初就基本上可以保證每月發行。1970年代被[[小羅伯特·普爾|小羅伯特·普爾]]等人買下，也因此得以更加穩定地出版。

2004年6月，《理性》的訂閱者都收到一份寫有他們自己名字的特殊的一刊，封面上還有他們家或者工作地點的[[卫星影像|衛星照相]]，以顯示公用數據庫的強大功能。<ref>{{cite news |title=Putting 40,000 Readers, One by One, on a Cover |url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9400E7D91139F936A35757C0A9629C8B63 |work=New York Times |date=April 5, 2004 |first=David |last=Carr |accessdate=October 20, 2010 |archive-date=2010-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100906142909/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9400E7D91139F936A35757C0A9629C8B63 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 這一舉動被《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》的大衛·凱爾（David Carr）稱作“用戶化出版的終極”和“不斷增加的數據庫的用法的經典展示”。 <ref>Carr, David. [http://www.nytimes.com/2004/04/05/business/05reason.html "Putting 40,000 Readers, One by One, on a Cover"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2004/04/05/business/05reason.html |date=20150901181947 }}. ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]''. April 5, 2004</ref>

2008年，《理性》的網站reason.com獲得[[威比獎|威比獎]]雜誌類獎。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.webbyawards.com/webbys/current_honorees.php?media_id=96&category_id=41&season=12 |title=Webby Honorees |publisher=Webbyawards.com |date= |accessdate=2009-06-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110607062130/http://www.webbyawards.com/webbys/current_honorees.php?media_id=96&category_id=41&season=12 |archivedate=2011-06-07 }}</ref>

== Hit and Run ==

Hit and Run（意為“肇事逃逸”）創立於2002年，是《理性》雜誌的[[博客|博客]]。由雜誌員工維護并發佈文章。創始之初[[尼克·吉萊斯皮|尼克·吉萊斯皮]]和後來的網站編輯[[蒂姆·卡瓦諾|蒂姆·卡瓦諾]]都是[[Suck.com|Suck.com]]的老手，并從這個網站得到了一些Hit and Run發展的靈感，他們還邀來了該網站的其他幾個寫手，因此該網站的諷刺性手法由此形成。<ref>{{cite news |first=Cynthia |last=Cotts |title=A Marriage Made Online: How 'Reason' Came to 'Suck' |url=http://www.villagevoice.com/news/0304,cotts,41332,6.html |work=The Village Voice |date=January 21, 2003 |accessdate=2013-07-02 |archive-date=2008-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080830081649/http://www.villagevoice.com/news/0304,cotts,41332,6.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2005年，該網站被《[[花花公子|花花公子]]》評為最佳政治博客之一。<ref>{{cite journal | title=Top 10 Political Blogs |journal=Playboy |date=November 2006}}</ref>

== Reason TV ==

Reason TV是隸屬於《理性》的一個網站，發布小型紀錄片和錄像評論。其上發佈過一系列著名諧星[[德魯·凱利|德魯·凱利]]主持的錄像節目。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://reason.org/news/show/reason-saves-cleveland-drew-carey |title=Reason Foundation on Reason Saves Cleveland |accessdate=October 20, 2010 |archive-date=2017-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170702151558/http://reason.org/news/show/reason-saves-cleveland-drew-carey |dead-url=no }}</ref>

